    "description": "<strong>A rage game that’s more than just a rage game. Dodge enemies, turrets, open doors, solve puzzles, get rewards and play with your friends.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve Puzzles!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148190/extras/82be8bea7390197190b46783eb8b91a3.poster.avif?t=1674603267\" width=692 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148190/extras/82be8bea7390197190b46783eb8b91a3.webm?t=1674603267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148190/extras/82be8bea7390197190b46783eb8b91a3.mp4?t=1674603267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Durus features a variety of puzzle elements that work together with obstacles to create an engaging and challenging experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reflex-based obstacles</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148190/extras/8a223e41e305edf03f80ee360972d6a8.poster.avif?t=1674603267\" width=692 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148190/extras/8a223e41e305edf03f80ee360972d6a8.webm?t=1674603267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148190/extras/8a223e41e305edf03f80ee360972d6a8.mp4?t=1674603267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Master the art of faking out a turret, use your surroundings for cover and use their cooldowns against them.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique puzzle elements</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148190/extras/00512513b79f55a352a8a1a7c3a45dbc.poster.avif?t=1674603267\" width=692 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148190/extras/00512513b79f55a352a8a1a7c3a45dbc.webm?t=1674603267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148190/extras/00512513b79f55a352a8a1a7c3a45dbc.mp4?t=1674603267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Puzzle elements like the subatomic circle change the whole game by shrinking your player.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tradition on its head</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148190/extras/11d7564484db7edb781a2ceece05bad7.poster.avif?t=1674603267\" width=692 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148190/extras/11d7564484db7edb781a2ceece05bad7.webm?t=1674603267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148190/extras/11d7564484db7edb781a2ceece05bad7.mp4?t=1674603267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Shields in Durus are a puzzle element, they are not their to help you survive.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer</h2>Play through the game's campaign co-operatively with your friends online or on the couch.<br>Or show off your skills in versus mode.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reflexes</h2>Fine-tuned levels that will get you saying &quot;no way that's possible!&quot; without feeling unfair.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzles</h2>Take a breath from the frustration to engage your brain and solve deceptively simple puzzles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level Editor</h2>Want to create the most infuriating level possible? Open our intuitive level editor and drag and drop until your vision is realised.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Workshop</h2>Ready to share your creation? Looking for a new challenge after the campaign? Upload your own or browse the workshop for custom levels to play by yourself or with friends.",
